	(2) Concessions and facilities to disabled employees:- Union told in clear terms to Director (HR) that the services of disabled personnel can neither be dispensed with nor reduced as per DOP guidelines. The DOT has not endorsed DOP communications to BSNL HQR. The Director (HR) agreed to the union’s plea and said the DOP guidelines will be followed even if these are not endorsed to BSNL by DOT.
