                                <font face="Arial" size="2">11-08-2017 :</font><font face="Arial" color="#0000FF" size="2"> Kind attention of all the circle Secretaries:- Dear Comrades you are aware that as per NEPP notification in 2010 the first upgradation to such officials who have regularized on or after 01-10-2000 will be granted after completion of 8 years of service from 01-10-2000. Some Comrades went to Court against this and Hon’ble Court has directed the BSNL management to grant upgradation to such regularized officials who were granted TSM on or before 01-10-2000 and regularized after formation of BSNL only from 01-10-2004 as it is done for other observed employees. On this verdict of Hon’ble Court the officials who were went to the Court got their upgradation revised with retrospective effect, now the management wants to extend it for others. (This issue was raised in Nation Council). This issue was discussed in BSNL management committee and the committee has directed the establishment branch to seek views of recognized unions in the matter as the management wants to implement this award of Court but they want to give it with prospective effect that is the pay fixation will be done notionally w.e.f. 01-10-2004 but the actual benefit will be from the date of approval of BSNL Board of this issue. Kindly send your suggestions within a week time to enable CHQ to take a decision in this regard and to convey, it to BSNL management by 18-08-2017.
     

